tion&#038;p=67',0,'certification','',0),(68,3,'2017-01-30 13:35:49','2017-01-30 13:35:49','','logo-img1','','inherit','open','closed','','logo-img1','','','2017-01-30 13:35:49','2017-01-30 13:35:49','',67,'http://lnjdenim.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/logo-img1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(69,3,'2017-02-01 06:07:11','2017-02-01 06:07:11','Weaving into the New Millennium','About','','inherit','closed','closed','','11-revision-v1','','','2017-02-01 06:07:11','2017-02-01 06:07:11','',11,'http://lnjdenim.in/11-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(70,3,'2017-02-01 06:26:59','2017-02-01 06:26:59','','about-page-banner-left','','inherit','open','closed','','about-page-banner-left','','','2017-02-01 06:26:59','2017-02-01 06:26:59','',11,'http://lnjdenim.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/about-page-banner-left.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(71,3,'2017-02-01 06:30:46','2017-02-01 06:30:46','<p>RSWM Limited is the flagship company of the LNJ Bhilwara group and a leader in the domestic and international textile industry. With a focus on innovation, commitment to excellence and rooted in sustainability, RSWM has established itself as a market leader and built strong partnerships across the globe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>LNJ Denim, a denim-manufacturing facility established in 2007 under RSWM Limited, has a manufacturing capacity of 32 million meters annually. Today, LNJ Denim is globally acknowledged for its exceptional quality, setting a high standard in the industry for top-notch service, continuous innovation, and trendsetting practices. We are committed to processes and technologies that support a sustainable business model and a greener environment.</p>','From Fibre to Finishing','','publish','closed','closed','','from-fibre-to-finishing','','','2025-03-11 10:31:00','2025-03-11 10:31:00','',11,'http://lnjdenim.in/?page_id=71',43,'page','',0),(72,3,'2017-02-01 06:30:46','2017-02-01 06:30:46','LNJ Denim’s manufacturing facility was established in 2007 as a part of RSWM Limited, the flagship company of LNJ Bhilwara Group,\r\nis one of the largest textile manufacturers in India and exports to over 78 countries around the world. Its 10 manufacturing plants, with\r\n505,000 spindles and 176 looms, produce high-quality cotton, mélange, synthetic and novelty yarns, along with suiting and denim fabrics.','From Fibre to Finishing','','inherit','closed','closed','','71-revision-v1','','','2017-02-01 06:30:46','2017-02-01 06:30:46','',71,'http://lnjdenim.in/71-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(74,3,'2017-02-01 07:23:28','2017-02-01 07:23:28','<p>Founded by the legendary Mr. L. N. Jhunjhunwala in the year 1960, the LNJ Bhilwara Group has today emerged as a leading well-diversified conglomerate with business interests such as textiles, graphite electrodes, power generation, power engineering consultancy and IT enabled services. Today, this USD 1 billion Group employs over 25,000 employees, and there are more than 20 production units all located at the most strategically advantageous locations in India. The Group, with its many arteries spread into Global Business Planet, takes another major step through LNJ Denim in the field of global denim industry.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\r\nTaking this passion for denim to next level, the LNJ Bhilwara Group has setup LNJ Denim, a unit under the aegis of RSWM Limited - a Bhilwara Group has setup LNJ Denim manufacturing and styling setting new trends in global fashion.</p>','LNJ BHILWARA GROUP','','publish','closed','closed','','lnj-bhilwara-group','','','2017-02-14 07:36:42','2017-02-14 07:36:42','',11,'http://lnjdenim.in/?page_id=74',44,'page','',0),(75,3,'2017-02-01 07:23:28','2017-02-01 07:23:28','Founded by L.N. Jhunjhunwala in 1961, LNJ Bhilwara Group has emerged as a diversified conglomerate with holdings in textiles, graphite electrodes, power generation, power engineering, consultant and information technology services. With more than 20production units, all strategically located in India, the US$1-billion group of companies employs over 25,000 people.Over the next 55 years, what began as a small textile mill in Bhilwara became a leader in the domestic and international textile industry, transforming Bhilwara into one of the most important textile hubs in India. LNJ Bhilwara Group’s success is based on the union of traditional values and an inherent sense of self-reliance and adaptability.','LNJ BHILWARA GROUP','','inherit','closed','closed','','74-revision-v1','','','2017-02-01 07:23:28','2017-02-01 07:23:28','',74,'http://lnjdenim.in/74-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(76,3,'2017-02-01 07:28:30','2017-02-01 07:28:30','L.N. Jhunjhunwala (standing at right) establishes first unit of RSWM','1961','First unit of RSWM','publish','closed','closed','','1961','','','2017-02-10 09:12:28','2017-02-10 09:12:28','',0,'http://lnjdenim.in/?post_type=historic-highlights&#038;p=76',0,'historic-highlights','',0),(80,3,'2017-02-01 07:31:41','2017-02-01 07:31:41','RSWM Limited opens a primary and secondary school inside the factory premises for the children of employees','1993','Primary and secondary school  ','publish','closed','closed','','1993','','','2017-02-10 11:24:47','2017-02-10 11:24:47','',0,'http://lnjdenim.in/?post_type=historic-highlights&#038;p=80',0,'historic-highlights','',0),(81,3,'2017-02-01 07:32:03','2017-02-01 07:32:03','RSWM Limited establishes Mandapam unit in Rajasthan to manufacture mélange yarns','1994','Mandapam unit in Rajasthan','publish','closed','closed','','1994','','','2017-02-10 12:40:31','2017-02-10 12:40:31','',0,'http://lnjdenim.in/?post_type=historic-highlights&#038;p=81',0,'historic-highlights','',0),(82,3,'2017-02-01 07:32:33','2017-02-01 07:32:33','RSWM Limited starts Wärtsilä captive power plant and generates inhouse power','1996','Wärtsilä captive power plant','publish','closed','closed','','1996','','','2017-02-10 11:29:51','2017-02-10 11:29:51','',0,'http://lnjdenim.in/?post_type=historic-highlights&#038;p=82',0,'historic-highlights','',0),(83,3,'2017-02-01 07:32:58','2017-02-01 07:32:58','RSWM Limited establishes LNJ Denim, obtains its first organic certification and opens second captive thermal power plant','2007','Establishes LNJ Denim','publish','closed','closed','','2007','','','2017-02-10 12:38:54','2017-02-10 12:38:54','',0,'http://lnjdenim.in/?post_type=historic-highlights&#038;p=83',0,'historic-highlights','',0),(84,3,'2017-02-01 07:33:23','2017-02-01 07:33:23','RSWM Limited establishes India’s most sophisticated automated spinning plant in Kharigram, marketing quality yarns under the name ULTIMA','2011','Automated spinning plant','publish','closed','closed','','2011','','','2017-02-10 11:29:51','2017-02-10 11:29:51','',0,'http://lnjdenim.in/?post_type=historic-highlights&#038;p=84',0,'historic-highlights','',0),(85,3,'2017-02-01 07:33:48','2017-02-01 07:33:48','RSWM Limited begins spinning green polyester fibre','2015','Green polyester fibre','publish','closed','closed','','2015','','','2017-02-01 07:35:06','2017-02-01 07:35:06','',0,'http://lnjdenim.in/?post_type=historic-highlights&#038;p=85',0,'historic-highlights','',0),(86,3,'2017-02-01 07:34:24','2017-02-01 07:34:24','RSWM Limited launches RSWM EDGE','2016','Launches RSWM <br>EDGE','publish','closed','closed','','2016','','','2017-02-10 11:29:53','2017-02-10 11:29:53','',0,'http://lnjdenim.in/?post_type=historic-highlights&#038;p=86',0,'historic-highlights','',0),(87,3,'2017-02-01 09:12:27','2017-02-01 09:12:27','LNJ Denim is committed to processes and technologies that help keep our environment green and our business sustainable.\r\nEucalyptus from sustainably managed plantations such as this one provide cellulose for lyocell, one of many fibres we can utilise in your denim.','Sustainability','','inherit','closed','closed','','9-revision-v1','','','2017-02-01 09:12:27','2017-02-01 09:12:27','',9,'http://lnjdenim.in/9-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(88,3,'2017-02-01 09:16:57','2017-02-01 09:16:57','The Global Recycled Standard (GRS) addresses input material verification, chain of custody, environmental principles, social requirements, and labelling for textile products made from recycled materials. It aims to bea full-product standard for recycled material content that balances rigor and practicality for the industry and end consumers.','LNJ DENIM ADHERES TO THE GLOBAL RECYCLE STANDARD','','publish','closed','closed','','lnj-adheres-to-the-global-recycle-standard','','','2017-02-03 09:37:06','2017-02-03 09:37:06','',9,'http://lnjdenim.in/?page_id=88',62,'page','',0),(89,3,'2017-02-01 09:16:47','2017-02-01 09:16:47','','global-recycled-logo','','inherit','open','closed','','global-recycled-logo','','','2017-02-01 09:16:47','2017-02-01 09:16:47','',88,'http://lnjdenim.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/global-recycled-logo.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(90,3,'2017-02-01 09:16:57','2017-02-01 09:16:57','The Global Recycled Standard (GRS) addresses input material verification, chain of custody, environmental principles, social requirements, and labelling for textile products made from recycled materials. It aims to bea full-product standard for recycled material content that balances rigor and practicality for the industry and end consumers.','LNJ ADHERES TO THE GLOBAL RECYCLE STANDARD','','inherit','closed','closed','','88-revision-v1','','','2017-02-01 09:16:57','2017-02-01 09:16:57','',88,'http://lnjdenim.in/88-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(93,3,'2017-02-01 09:21:37','2017-02-01 09:21:37','','sustain-buketcenter-img','','inherit','open','closed','','sustain-buketcenter-img','','','2017-02-01 09:21:37','2017-02-01 09:21:37','',9,'http://lnjdenim.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/sustain-buketcenter-img.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(94,3,'2017-02-01 09:22:31','2017-02-01 09:22:31','We proudly offer recycled denim products in both rigid and stretch constructions. Our state-of-the-art Garnett machines efficiently break down post-consumer waste fabrics and convert them into new usable fibres—we’re weaving new denim while eliminating excess waste from landfills.','PRODUCTION BY RECYCLING','','publish','closed','closed','','production-by-recycling','','','2017-02-01 09:31:05','2017-02-01 09:31:05','',9,'http://lnjdenim.in/?page_id=94',61,'page','',0),(95,3,'2017-02-01 09:22:31','2017-02-01 09:22:31','<div class=\"col span_4 wow fadeInLeft\">\r\n<div class=\"sustain-three-buket sustain-first-box\">\r\n<div class=\"sustain-buket-absoltue\">\r\n<div class=\"sustain-buket-tabel\">\r\n<div class=\"sustain-buket-tabelcell\">\r\n\r\nWe proudly offer recycled denim products in both rigid and stretch constructions. Our state-of-the-art Garnett machines efficiently break down post-consumer waste fabrics and convert them into new usable fibres—we’re weaving new denim while eliminating excess waste from landfills.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','PRODUCTION BY RECYCLING','','inherit','closed','closed','','94-revision-v1','','','2017-02-01 09:22:31','2017-02-01 09:22:31','',94,'http://lnjdenim.in/94-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(96,3,'2017-02-01 09:23:02','2017-02-01 09:23:02','We also offer fabrics dyed with advanced techniques that use less water and fewer chemicals. To round out our efforts, we treat all of our post-process water in our own effluent treatment plant and further purify it via reverse osmosis before returning it to the environment cleaner than before.','SUSTAINABLE  WATER MANAGEMENT','','publish','closed','closed','','sustainable-water-management','','','2017-02-03 07:43:10','2017-02-03 07:43:10','',9,'http://lnjdenim.in/?page_id=96',63,'page','',0),(97,3,'2017-02-01 09:23:02','2017-02-01 09:23:02','We also offer fabrics dyed with advanced techniques that use less water and fewerchemicals. To round out our efforts, we treat all of our post-process water in our own effluent treatment plant and further purify it via reverse osmosis before returning it to the environment cleaner than before.','SUSTAINABLE  WATER MANAGEMENT','','inherit','closed','closed','','96-revision-v1','','','2017-02-01 09:23:02','2017-02-01 09:23:02','',96,'http://lnjdenim.in/96-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(98,3,'2017-02-01 09:31:05','2017-02-01 09:31:05','We proudly offer recycled denim products in both rigid and stretch constructions. Our state-of-the-art Garnett machines efficiently break down post-consumer waste fabrics and convert them into new usable fibres—we’re weaving new denim while eliminating excess waste from landfills.','PRODUCTION BY RECYCLING','','inherit','closed','closed','','94-revision-v1','','','2017-02-01 09:31:05','2017-02-01 09:31:05','',94,'http://lnjdenim.in/94-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(99,3,'2017-02-01 09:32:38','2017-02-01 09:32:38','','technology-page-banner-left','','inherit','open','closed','','technology-page-banner-left','','','2017-02-01 09:32:38','2017-02-01 09:32:38','',7,'http://lnjdenim.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/technology-page-banner-left.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(100,3,'2017-02-01 09:41:41','2017-02-01 09:41:41','We support our clients’ creativity with state-of-theart machinery. LNJ Denim employs skilled textile engineers to operate our world-class equipment. Assafety is our priority, our facilities are well-lit, airconditioned and clean. We adhere to strict safety standards and our factories have achieved OHSAS18001 and SA-8000 certificates.\n\n&nbsp;','Technology & Innovation','','inherit','closed','closed','','7-autosave-v1','','','2017-02-01 09:41:41','2017-02-01 09:41:41','',7,'http://lnjdenim.in/7-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(101,3,'2017-02-01 09:41:44','2017-02-01 09:41:44','We support our clients’ creativity with state-of-theart machinery. LNJ Denim employs skilled textile engineers to operate our world-class equipment. Assafety is our priority, our facilities are well-lit, airconditioned and clean. We adhere to strict safety standards and our factories have achieved OHSAS18001 and SA-8000 certificates.\r\n\r\nRSWM Limited has earned The Synthe