osed','','lightness-img1','','','2017-02-13 05:37:39','2017-02-13 05:37:39','',158,'http://lnjdenim.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/lightness-img1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(255,3,'2017-02-13 06:25:21','2017-02-13 06:25:21','','Spring/summer 2018','','inherit','closed','closed','','141-revision-v1','','','2017-02-13 06:25:21','2017-02-13 06:25:21','',141,'http://lnjdenim.in/141-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(256,3,'2017-02-13 06:26:25','2017-02-13 06:26:25','','Spring/Summer 2018','','inherit','closed','closed','','141-revision-v1','','','2017-02-13 06:26:25','2017-02-13 06:26:25','',141,'http://lnjdenim.in/141-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(257,3,'2017-02-13 07:04:09','2017-02-13 07:04:09','Having developed our own in-house capability of producing PCW recycled denim fabric in both rigid and stretch we have invested in garneting equipment which convert used garments and fabric waste to this end. Many of our products are developed using \"Advanced Denim\" processes which consume less water, less chemicals, and less energy in the manufacturing and washing. In addition we are promoting our \"Forever Raw\" denims which use no water at all in the laundry thereby reducing the use of chemicals and energy as well. For non cotton fibres we use certified PET recycled polyesters, Eco made Coolmax and Thermolite. As well as using our own recycled cotton; organic cotton we use 100% BCI cotton.','Taking Care','','inherit','closed','closed','','160-revision-v1','','','2017-02-13 07:04:09','2017-02-13 07:04:09','',160,'http://lnjdenim.in/160-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(258,3,'2017-02-13 07:07:05','2017-02-13 07:07:05','<p>\r\nWe support our clients’ creativity with state-of-the art machinery. LNJ Denim employs skilled textile engineers to operate our world-class equipment. As safety is our priority, our facilities are well-lit, airconditioned and clean. We adhere to strict safety standards and our factories have achieved OHSAS18001 and SA-8000 certificates. We at the LNJ denim plant, use state-of-the-art machinery to create your fabric dreams into reality.\r\n\r\n</p>','Plant','','inherit','closed','closed','','7-revision-v1','','','2017-02-13 07:07:05','2017-02-13 07:07:05','',7,'http://lnjdenim.in/7-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(260,3,'2017-02-14 07:12:37','2017-02-14 07:12:37','Founded by the legendary Mr. L. N. Jhunjhunwala in the year 1960, the LNJ Bhilwara Group has today emerged as a leading well-diversified conglomerate with business interests such as textiles, graphite electrodes, power generation, power engineering consultancy and IT enabled services. Today, this USD 1 billion Group employs over 25,000 employees, and there are more than 20 production units all located at the most strategically advantageous locations in India. The Group, with its many arteries spread into Global Business Planet, takes another major step through LNJ Denim in the field of global industry.<br>\r\n\r\nTaking this passion for denim to next level, the LNJ Bhilwara Group has setup LNJ Denim, a unit under the aegis of RSWM Limited - a Bhilwara Group has setup LNJ Denim manufacturing and styling setting new trends in global fashion.','From Fibre to Finishing','','inherit','closed','closed','','71-revision-v1','','','2017-02-14 07:12:37','2017-02-14 07:12:37','',71,'http://lnjdenim.in/71-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(261,3,'2017-02-14 07:16:45','2017-02-14 07:16:45','Founded by the legendary Mr. L. N. Jhunjhunwala in the year 1960, the LNJ Bhilwara Group has today emerged as a leading well-diversified conglomerate with business interests such as textiles, graphite electrodes, power generation, power engineering consultancy and IT enabled services.<br> Today, this USD 1 billion Group employs over 25,000 employees, and there are more than 20 production units all located at the most strategically advantageous locations in India. <br>The Group, with its many arteries spread into Global Business Planet, takes another major step through LNJ Denim in the field of global denim industry.<br>\r\n\r\nTaking this passion for denim to next level, the LNJ Bhilwara Group has setup LNJ Denim, a unit under the aegis of RSWM Limited - a Bhilwara Group has setup LNJ Denim manufacturing and styling setting new trends in global fashion.\r\n','From Fibre to Finishing','','inherit','closed','closed','','71-revision-v1','','','2017-02-14 07:16:45','2017-02-14 07:16:45','',71,'http://lnjdenim.in/71-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(262,3,'2017-02-14 07:21:12','2017-02-14 07:21:12','LNJ Denim, a denim-manufacturing facility established in 2007 under RSWM Limited (the flagship company of LNJ Bhilwara Group), has a manufacturing capacity of 25 million metres annually. LNJ Denim has earned an excellent reputation amongst international and domestic brands as an innovator and a quality supplier of denim fabric.','From Fibre to Finishing','','inherit','closed','closed','','71-revision-v1','','','2017-02-14 07:21:12','2017-02-14 07:21:12','',71,'http://lnjdenim.in/71-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(264,3,'2017-02-14 07:24:25','2017-02-14 07:24:25','Founded by the legendary Mr. L. N. Jhunjhunwala in the year 1960, the LNJ Bhilwara Group has today emerged as a leading well-diversified conglomerate with business interests such as textiles, graphite electrodes, power generation, power engineering consultancy and IT enabled services. Today, this USD 1 billion Group employs over 25,000 employees, and there are more than 20 production units all located at the most strategically advantageous locations in India. The Group, with its many arteries spread into Global Business Planet, takes another major step through LNJ Denim in the field of global denim industry.\r\n\r\nTaking this passion for denim to next level, the LNJ Bhilwara Group has setup LNJ Denim, a unit under the aegis of RSWM Limited - a Bhilwara Group has setup LNJ Denim manufacturing and styling setting new trends in global fashion.','LNJ BHILWARA GROUP','','inherit','cl