ims of old. A new wave of high profile twills which grab a finish showing off the high low contrast in finishing speak loudly of old timer indigos. In addition, 2x1 is making a comeback in textured oe looks and no slubs washing to a perfect vintage. Our vintage denims also boast the orinigal selvedge for added authenticity.','Boss of the Road','','inherit','closed','closed','','162-revision-v1','','','2017-02-24 04:48:36','2017-02-24 04:48:36','',162,'http://lnjdenim.in/162-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(275,3,'2017-02-27 11:46:42','2017-02-27 11:46:42','','ojg','','publish','closed','closed','','ojg','','','2017-02-27 11:46:42','2017-02-27 11:46:42','',0,'http://lnjdenim.in/?post_type=client&#038;p=275',0,'client','',0),(276,3,'2017-02-27 11:46:09','2017-02-27 11:46:09','','ojg','','inherit','open','closed','','ojg','','','2017-02-27 11:46:09','2017-02-27 11:46:09','',275,'http://lnjdenim.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/ojg.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(277,3,'2017-02-27 11:47:56','2017-02-27 11:47:56','','jcp','','publish','closed','closed','','jcp','','','2017-02-27 11:56:18','2017-02-27 11:56:18','',0,'http://lnjdenim.in/?post_type=client&#038;p=277',0,'client','',0),(278,3,'2017-02-27 11:47:38','2017-02-27 11:47:38','','jcp','','inherit','open','closed','','jcp','','','2017-02-27 11:47:38','2017-02-27 11:47:38','',277,'http://lnjdenim.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/jcp.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(279,3,'2017-02-27 11:49:10','2017-02-27 11:49:10','','jordaache','','publish','closed','closed','','jordaache','','','2017-02-27 11:54:22','2017-02-27 11:54:22','',0,'http://lnjdenim.in/?post_type=client&#038;p=279',0,'client','',0),(280,3,'2017-02-27 11:48:53','2017-02-27 11:48:53','','jordaache','','inherit','open','closed','','jordaache','','','2017-02-27 11:48:53','2017-02-27 11:48:53','',279,'http://lnjdenim.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/jordaache.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(281,3,'2017-02-27 11:53:52','2017-02-27 11:53:52','','jordaache',