Gartex-Texprocess-mumbail','','inherit','open','closed','','gartex-texprocess-mumbail','','','2022-11-23 07:57:15','2022-11-23 07:57:15','',595,'http://lnjdenim.in/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Gartex-Texprocess-mumbail.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(597,3,'2022-11-23 08:24:02','2022-11-23 08:24:02','It is a great pleasure to meet visitors and business partners at the Premiere Vision Denim show. They provide a window to the world of denim, its trends, its market, its culture and, of course, its community.\r\nWe are really thankful for your precious time and hope that we will have long term business affiliation.','PREMIERE VISION DENIM','','publish','open','closed','','premiere-vision-denim','','','2022-11-23 10:52:02','2022-11-23 10:52:02','',0,'http://lnjdenim.in/?post_type=events&#038;p=597',4,'events','',0),(598,3,'2022-11-23 08:23:46','2022-11-23 08:23:46','','berlin','','inherit','open','closed','','berlin','','','2022-11-23 08:23:46','2022-11-23 08:23:46','',597,'http://lnjdenim.in/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/berlin.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(599,3,'2022-11-23 08:28:36','2022-11-23 08:28:36','Meeting our clients and business partners during the exhibition was a rewarding experience. We\'d want to thank you for all the love you\'ve shown us over the past two days. This only serves to encourage us to develop new and inventive items.','DENIM AND JEANS INDIA SHOW','','publish','open','closed','','denimandjeans-india-show','','','2022-11-23 12:11:04','2022-11-23 12:11:04','',0,'http://lnjdenim.in/?post_type=events&#038;p=599',3,'events','',0),(600,3,'2022-11-23 08:28:13','2022-11-23 08:28:13','','bengluru','','inherit','open','closed','','bengluru','','','2022-11-23 08:28:13','2022-11-23 08:28:13','',599,'http://lnjdenim.in/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/bengluru.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(601,3,'2022-11-23 08:32:31','2022-11-23 08:32:31','A truly spectacular opening with a whole three days of networking, business deals and more! Businesses are built by people and for people. This Exhibition left us floored with the kind of response, interactions, and engagement we received from our client & business Partners.','GARTEX TEXPROCESS','','publish','open','closed','','gartex-texprocess-2','','','2022-11-23 12:10:44','2022-11-23 12:10:44','',0,'http://lnjdenim.in/?post_type=events&#038;p=601',2,'events','',0),(602,3,'2022-11-23 08:32:15','2022-11-23 08:32:15','','Delhi','','inherit','open','closed','','delhi','','','2022-11-23 08:32:15','2022-11-23 08:32:15','',601,'http://lnjdenim.in/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Delhi.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(603,3,'2022-11-23 08:37:03','2022-11-23 08:37:03','At the Denimsandjeans Japan Show, it is a pleasure to interact with attendees and potential business partners. When it comes to denim, Japan is one of the most lucrative countries with significant organizations and merchants. The Japanese have advanced the art of denim production, inspiring customers, designers, and suppliers around the world.\r\n\r\nWe were astounded by the level of response, interactions, and engagement, we saw from our clients and business partners throughout this exhibition. We sincerely appreciate you taking the time to read this, and we look forward to doing business with you in the future.','DENIMS AND JEANS JAPAN','','publish','open','closed','','denimsandjeans-japan','','','2022-11-23 12:35:42','2022-11-23 12:35:42','',0,'http://lnjdenim.in/?post_type=events&#038;p=603',0,'events','',0),(604,3,'2022-11-23 08:35:47','2022-11-23 08:35:47','','JAPAN','','inherit','open','closed','','japan','','','2022-11-23 08:35:47','2022-11-23 08:35:47','',603,'http://lnjdenim.in/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/JAPAN.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(608,3,'2022-11-23 11:53:55','2022-11-23 11:53:55','At the Denimsandjeans Japan Show, it is a pleasure to interact with attendees and potential business partners. When it comes to denim, Japan is one of the most lucrative countries with significant organizations and merchants. The Japanese have advanced the art of denim production, inspiring customers, designers, and suppliers around the world.\n\nWe were astounded by the level of response, interactions, and engagement, we saw from our clients and business partners throughout this exhibition. We sincerely appreciate you taking the time to read this, and we look forward to doing business with you in the future.','DENIMS AND JEANS JAPAN','','inherit','closed','closed','','603-autosave-v1','','','2022-11-23 11:53:55','2022-11-23 11:53:55','',603,'http://lnjdenim.in/603-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(609,3,'2022-11-23 12:09:14','2022-11-23 12:09:14','','gartec-india','','inherit','open','closed','','gartec-india','','','2022-11-23 12:09:14','2022-11-23 12:09:14','',0,'http://lnjdenim.in/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/gartec-india.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(610,3,'2022-11-23 12:09:17','2022-11-23 12:09:17','','india','','inherit','open','closed','','india','','','2022-11-23 12:09:17','2022-11-23 12:09:17','',0,'http://lnjdenim.in/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/india.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(611,3,'2022-11-23 12:09:20','2022-11-23 12:09:20','','japan','','inherit','open','closed','','japan-2','','','2022-11-23 12:09:20','2022-11-23 12:09:20','',0,'http://lnjdenim.in/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/japan-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(612,3,'2022-11-23 12:09:26','2022-11-23 12:09:26','','gartec-india','','inherit','open','closed','','gartec-india-2','','','2022-11-23 12:09:26','2022-11-23 12:09:26','',0,'http://lnjdenim.in/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/gartec-india-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(615,3,'2023-02-20 05:07:11','2023-02-20 05:07:11','','Spring/Summer 2024','','publish','closed','closed','','switch-ss24','','','2023-02-23 05:08:15','2023-02-23 05:08:15','',5,'http://lnjdenim.in/?page_id=615',8,'page','',0),(616,3,'2023-02-20 05:07:11','2023-02-20 05:07:11','','Switch','','inherit','closed','closed','','615-revision-v1','','','2023-02-20 05:07:11'