ur cutting-edge denim solutions, \r\ndesigned to meet the evolving needs of the fashion industry. \r\nWe extend our heartfelt thanks to everyone who visited our booth and look forward to continuing to drive innovation in the denim world.\r\n','Gartex Texprocess India','','publish','closed','closed','','1498-2','','','2024-10-19 06:29:15','2024-10-19 06:29:15','',0,'https://lnjdenim.in/?post_type=events&#038;p=1498',0,'events','',0),(1499,3,'2024-10-19 06:17:34','2024-10-19 06:17:34','','5ff8218e4914e_Denim-Logo','','inherit','open','closed','','5ff8218e4914e_denim-logo','','','2024-10-19 06:17:34','2024-10-19 06:17:34','',1498,'https://lnjdenim.in/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/5ff8218e4914e_Denim-Logo.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(1500,3,'2024-10-19 06:22:57','2024-10-19 06:22:57','','denim-show-logo','','inherit','open','closed','','denim-show-logo','','','2024-10-19 06:22:57','2024-10-19 06:22:57','',1498,'https://lnjdenim.in/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/denim-show-logo.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1501,3,'2024-10-19 06:24:40','2024-10-19 06:24:40','We were thrilled to be part of Gartex Texprocess India, held from February 1st-3rd, 2024, at the Jio World Convention Center, \nMumbai, Pavilion 1, Booth B15. This event provided an exciting platform to showcase our latest innovations in denim for the Autumn/Winter 2025 season, \nhighlighting sustainable fabrics, advanced technologies, and new washes. Attendees had the opportunity to explore our cutting-edge denim solutions, \ndesigned to meet the evolving needs of the fashion industry. \nWe extend our heartfelt thanks to everyone who visited our booth and look forward to continuing to drive innovation in the denim world.\n','Gartex Texprocess','','inherit','closed','closed','','1498-autosave-v1','','','2024-10-19 06:24:40','2024-10-19 06:24:40','',1498,'https://lnjdenim.in/?p=1501',0,'revision','',0),(1502,3,'2024-10-19 06:26:24','2024-10-19 06:26:24','We are excited to have participated in the Denim and Jeans Show on March 26-27, 2024, at Hamamatsucho-kan, Tokyo (Booth No. 6). \r\nThis event marked a special occasion as we unveiled a unique garment collaboration with Shell Apparels, \r\nblending our expertise in denim with their innovative apparel designs. Together, we showcased our latest denim collection for Autumn/Winter 2025, \r\nfeaturing cutting-edge fabrics and sustainable production techniques. \r\nWe were thrilled to connect with industry leaders and showcase how our partnership is pushing the boundaries of denim fashion. \r\nThank you to everyone who visited and supported us!','Denim and Jeans Show JAPAN','','publish','closed','closed','','denim-and-jeans-show-japan','','','2024-10-19 06:28:28','2024-10-19 06:28:28','',0,'https://lnjdenim.in/?post_type=events&#038;p=1502',0,'events','',0),(1503,3,'2024-10-19 06:27:10','2024-10-19 06:27:10','','japan-1','','inherit','open','closed','','japan-1','','','2024-10-19 06:27:10','2024-10-19 06:27:10','',1502,'https://lnjdenim.in/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/japan-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1504,3,'2024-10-19 06:33:40','2024-10-19 06:33:40','We were excited to participate in the Bangladesh Denim Expo on May 6th and 7th at ICCB, Bashundhara, where we revealed our latest Autumn/Winter 2025 collection, \r\nECHO, at Booth No. 44. This collection showcases a blend of innovation and sustainability, with cutting-edge fabric technologies and eco-conscious practices. \r\nVisitors explored new denim washes, advanced fibers, and design trends that reflect our commitment to the future of denim. We thank everyone who visited our booth \r\nand showed interest in ECHO, and we look forward to driving further innovation in the denim industry.\r\n','Bangladesh Denim Expo','','publish','closed','closed','','bangladesh-denim-expo','','','2024-10-19 06:33:40','2024-10-19 06:33:40','',0,'https://lnjdenim.in/?post_type=events&#038;p=1504',0,'events','',0),(1505,3,'2024-10-19 06:32:02','2024-10-19 06:32:02','','logo','','inherit','open','closed','','logo','','','2024-10-19 06:32:02','2024-10-19 06:32:02','',1504,'https://lnjdenim.in/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/logo.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1506,3,'2024-10-19 06:37:55','2024-10-19 06:37:55','We are excited to have participated in the Denims and Jeans Show on May 15-16, 2024, at The Lalit Ashok, Bengaluru (Booth No. K-27). \r\nAt this event, we unveiled our latest Autumn/Winter 2025 denim collection, featuring innovative designs, sustainable fabrics, \r\nand the newest trends in washes and finishes. \r\nIt was a fantastic opportunity to connect with industry professionals and showcase our commitment to eco-conscious and trend-forward denim solutions. \r\nWe sincerely thank everyone who visited our booth and engaged with our collection, and we look forward to continuing to inspire and innovate in the denim industry.\r\n\r\n','Denims and Jeans Show','','publish','closed','closed','','denims-and-jeans-show','','','2024-10-19 06:37:55','2024-10-19 06:37:55','',0,'https://lnjdenim.in/?post_type=events&#038;p=1506',0,'events','',0),(1507,3,'2024-10-19 06:36:13','2024-10-19 06:36:13','','dji-logo','','inherit','open','closed','','dji-logo','','','2024-10-19 06:36:13','2024-10-19 06:36:13','',1506,'https://lnjdenim.in/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dji-logo.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1508,3,'2024-10-19 06:42:40','2024-10-19 06:42:40','We were thrilled to showcase our latest innovations at Gartex Texprocess India, held from August 1st-3rd, 2024, at YashoBhoomi (IICC), \r\nDwarka, Delhi, Booth M05. This event gave us the opportunity to present our cutting-edge Autumn/Winter 2025 denim collections, \r\nblending sustainable practices and advanced technologies. Attendees explored our latest developments in fabrics, \r\nwashes, and eco-friendly techniques that set new trends in the denim industry. \r\nWe extend our gratitude to all visitors who engaged with our collections, and we remain committed to shaping the future of denim through \r\ninnovation and sustainability.\r\n','Gartex Texprocess India','','publish','closed','closed','','gartex-texprocess-india','','','2024-10-19 06:45:12','2024-10-19 06:45:12','',0,'https://lnjdenim.in/?post_type=events&#038;p=1508',0,'events','',0),(1509,3,'2024-10-19 06:39:58','2024-10-19 06:39:58','','denim-show-logo','','inherit','open','closed','','denim-show-logo-2','','','2024-10-19 06:39:58','2024-10-19 06:39:58','',1508,'https://lnjdenim.in/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/denim-show-logo-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1510,3,'2024-10-19 08:12:52','2024-10-19 08:12:52','','SS 26','','publish','closed','closed','','ss-26','','','2024-11-21 18:06:46','2024-11-21 18:06:46','',5,'https://lnjdenim.in/?page_id=1510',0,'page','',0),(1511,3,'2024-10-19 08:12:52','2024-10-19 08:12:52','','SS 26','','inherit','closed','closed','','1510-revision-v1','','','2024-10-19 08:12:52','2024-10-19 08:12:52','',1510,'https://lnjdenim.in/?p=1511',0,'revision','',0),(1514,3,'2025-12-15 20:17:40','2024-11-21 18:06:25',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','1514','','','2025-12-15 20:17:40','2025-12-15 20:17:40','',5,'https://lnjdenim.in/?p=1514',4,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1517,3,'2025-03-11 10:29:28','2025-03-11 10:29:28','RSWM Limited is the flagship company of the LNJ Bhilwara group and a leader in the domestic and international textile industry. With a focus on innovation, commitment to excellence and rooted in sustainability, RSWM has established itself as a market leader and built strong partnerships across the globe.\r\n\r\nLNJ Denim, a denim-manufacturing facility established in 2007 under RSWM Limited, has a manufacturing capacity of 32 million meters annually. Today, LNJ Denim is globally acknowledged for its exceptional quality, setting a high standard in the industry for top-notch service, continuous innovation, and trendsetting practices. We are committed to processes and technologies that support a sustainable business model and a greener environment.','From Fibre to Finishing','','inherit','closed','closed','','71-revision-v1','','','2025-03-11 10:29:28','2025-03-11 10:29:28','',71,'https://lnjdenim.in/?p=1517',0,'revision','',0),(1518,3,'2025-03-11 10:31:00','2025-03-11 10:31:00','<p>RSWM Limited is the flagship company of the LNJ Bhilwara group and a leader in the domestic and international textile industry. With a focus on innovation, commitment to excellence and rooted in sustainability, RSWM has established itself as a market leader and built strong partnerships across the globe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>LNJ Denim, a denim-manufacturing facility established in 2007 under RSWM Limited, has a manufacturing capacity of 32 million meters annually. Today, LNJ Denim is globally acknowledged for its exceptional quality, setting a high standard in the industry for top-notch service, continuous innovation, and trendsetting practices. We are committed to processes and technologies that support a sustainable business model and a greener environment.</p>','From Fibre to Finishing','','inherit','closed','closed','','71-revision-v1','','','2025-03-11 10:31:00','2025-03-11 10:31:00','',71,'https://lnjdenim.in/?p=1518',0,'revision','',0),(1520,3,'2025-05-04 17:45:13','2025-05-04 17:45:13','','AW26','','publish','closed','closed','','aw-26','','','2025-05-04 17:47:00','2025-05-04 17:47:00','',5,'https://lnjdenim.in/?page_id=1520',0,'page','',0),(1521,3,'2025-05-04 17:45:13','2025-05-04 17:45:13','','AW26','','inherit','closed','closed','','1520-revision-v1','','','2025-05-04 17:45:13','2025-05-04 17:45:13','',1520,'https://lnjdenim.in/?p=1521',0,'revision','',0),(1523,3,'2025-12-15 20:17:40','2025-05-13 16:53:16',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','1523','','','2025-12-15 20:17:40','2025-12-15 20:17:40','',5,'https://lnjdenim.in/?p=1523',3,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1524,3,'2025-05-14 05:50:22','2025-05-14 05:50:22','That’s a Wrap on Denimsandjeans India 2025!\r\n\r\nOur LNJ Denim booth continued to draw incredible energy from clients, collaborators 